    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The conferring of recognition or esteem upon someone or an organization, often but not always in recognition of an accomplishment, merit, or professional or social rank. The honor often has a name or title associated with it. For recognition accompanied by remuneration, use "honoraria" or "awards." </Note_Text>
